<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٥٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ابن المسيب عن ابن <span class="c2">(عمر)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> قال: الحكرة خطيئة <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
